title: Frank Lloyd Wright Mirror—Marin County Civic Center
description:
Living in a Frank Lloyd Wright® (American, 1867–1959) frame of mind, this mirror reflects his unflinching architectural style. Made of laser cut cherry wood and assembled by hand in the USA. Hanging hardware included. 

25 in. diam. x ½ in.
